### Register a New User and Company
POST http://localhost:4000/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyName": "Kenya Bottlers Ltd",
  "userName": "Jane Doe",
  "email": "jane.doe@kenyabottlers.com",
  "password": "securepassword123"
}

###
### Login with existing user credentials
# @name login 
POST http://localhost:4000/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "jane.doe@kenyabottlers.com",
  "password": "securepassword123"
}

###
### Add a new machine (requires authentication)
# @name createMachine
POST http://localhost:4000/machines
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "Filling Machine C-4",
  "location": "Bottling Hall 2"
}

###
### Get all machines for the logged-in user's company
GET http://localhost:4000/machines
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

###
### Report a machine breakdown
POST http://localhost:4000/breakdowns
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "machineId": 1,
  "description": "The main conveyor belt is jammed and making a loud grinding noise."
}

###
### Get all active breakdowns for the company
GET http://localhost:4000/breakdowns
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

###
### Update the status of a specific breakdown
# Change the '1' in the URL to a valid breakdown ID from the GET request above
PATCH http://localhost:4000/breakdowns/3/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "status": "Acknowledged"
}

###
### (UTILITIES) Define a new utility for the company
POST http://localhost:4000/utilities
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "Mains Power Meter",
  "unit": "kWh"
}

###
### (UTILITIES) Get all utilities for the company
GET http://localhost:4000/utilities
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

###
### (UTILITIES) Submit a new meter reading
POST http://localhost:4000/utility-readings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "utilityId": 1,
  "readingValue": 2580.50
}

###
### (UTILITIES) Get reading history for a specific utility
# Change the '1' in the URL to a valid utility ID
GET http://localhost:4000/utilities/1/readings
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

###
### (PREVENTIVE MAINTENANCE) Schedule a new task
POST http://localhost:4000/preventive-maintenance
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "machineId": 1,
  "taskDescription": "Monthly calibration and sensor check",
  "frequencyDays": 30,
  "startDate": "2025-10-15"
}

###
### (PREVENTIVE MAINTENANCE) Get all scheduled tasks
GET http://localhost:4000/preventive-maintenance
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}